      <title>美国钢铁工会拒绝新日铁的信件，称其为“毫无意义的纸”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/usw-rejects-nippon-steel-letter-as-meaningless-piece-of-paper</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国钢铁工人联合会驳斥了新日铁公司承诺支出和就业保护的信函，称其为“一纸空文”，这是对日本钢铁制造商计划以 141 亿美元收购美国钢铁公司的最新一轮攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/usw-rejects-nippon-steel-letter-as-meaningless-piece-of-paper</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 17:30:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果反对派协议失败，南非 IFP 可能加入 ANC 政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/s-africa-s-ifp-may-join-anc-government-if-opposition-pact-fails</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非反对党因卡塔自由党表示，如果执政党未能在下个月的选举中赢得绝对多数，将考虑与非洲人国民大会组成政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/s-africa-s-ifp-may-join-anc-government-if-opposition-pact-fails</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 17:27:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摇摆州 1140 亿美元的通货膨胀削减法案工厂投资中的一半净额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/swing-states-net-half-of-114-billion-in-ira-factory-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新能源财经报道，自 2022 年《通胀削减法案》通过以来，制造商已宣布了约 1140 亿美元的清洁技术投资，其中几乎一半支出来自政治摇摆州。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/swing-states-net-half-of-114-billion-in-ira-factory-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 17:19:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国极右翼选择党正在调查涉嫌与俄罗斯有联系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/german-far-right-afd-party-looking-into-alleged-russia-links</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国高级选择党官员计划就两名极右翼政党议员涉嫌与全欧洲亲俄虚假信息网络的联系进行质询。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/german-far-right-afd-party-looking-into-alleged-russia-links</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 16:25:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度考虑制定天然气发电紧急规则以满足夏季需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/india-mulls-emergency-rules-for-gas-power-to-meet-sumer-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度电力部将考虑援引紧急规则在夏季运行燃气发电厂，这是确保供应不间断的一系列措施的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/india-mulls-emergency-rules-for-gas-power-to-meet-sumer-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 16:18:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰总统签署法律将入伍年龄降至25岁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/ukrainian-president-signs-law-to-reduce-wartime-conscription-age</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基 (Volodymyr Zelenskiy) 签署了一项将战时征兵年龄降至 25 岁的法案，但由于基辅军队难以抵御俄罗斯的进攻，该法案推迟了立法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/ukrainian-president-signs-law-to-reduce-wartime-conscription-age</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 16:00:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登、习近平通电话谈论人工智能风险、俄罗斯和芬太尼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/biden-xi-spoke-by-phone-to-manage-world-tensions-opportunities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登和中国国家主席习近平周二通电话，这是自去年 11 月在加州会晤以来他们的首次一对一沟通。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/biden-xi-spoke-by-phone-to-manage-world-tensions-opportunities</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 15:30:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约提议设立1000亿美元五年基金援助乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/nato-proposes-100-billion-five-year-fund-to-support-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约秘书长延斯·斯托尔滕贝格提议在五年内为乌克兰建立一个价值 1000 亿美元的盟国捐款基金，作为联盟领导人 7 月齐聚华盛顿时签署的一揽子计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/nato-proposes-100-billion-five-year-fund-to-support-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 15:10:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国食品援助组织称工人在加沙罢工中丧生</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/aid-workers-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-gaza-jose-andres-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据著名厨师何塞·安德烈斯 (José Andrés) 创立的救灾组织 X 上发布的消息称，世界中央厨房 (World Central Kitchen) 的 7 名救援人员在以色列军队对加沙的空袭中丧生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-02/aid-workers-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-gaza-jose-andres-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 00:26:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最终医疗保险优惠率令人失望，健康保险公司股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/final-medicare-advantage-notice-shows-no-boost-from-initial-rate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二震撼医疗保险公司股票的医疗保险支付决定为拜登政府带来了一场高风险的选举年赌博，因为老年人最终可能会在选举日之前看到他们的医疗计划被削减。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/final-medicare-advantage-notice-shows-no-boost-from-initial-rate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 20:32:03 GMT</pubDate>
